<plot>Perspective is a story of two men. On this day, they both meet and see the same people, see and hear the same things. But if you were to ask each of them how their day was, they would have two entirely different stories. Both would be telling the truth, but the truth exists only in one's own unique perspective.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?429849</url></doc>
